      "range": "3356-3418",
      "markText": "除了大概的方向，他不知道自己将走向哪里，但他明白稍后他会知道的。他从容地纵马向前，感觉身后太阳冉冉升起，使得空气也坚硬起来。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019348&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=3356&rangeEnd=3418",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55732e90716e81945571fcf?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=3356&rangeEnd=3418"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019348_7_6848-6916",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "6848-6916",
      "markText": "他相信——并且一直以来都相信，自然界有一种微妙的磁力，不会对他的人生轨迹无动于衷，如果他不知不觉地听从它的召唤，它会把他引到正确的方向。",
      "totalCount": 143,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019348&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6848&rangeEnd=6916",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55732e90716e81945571fcf?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6848&rangeEnd=6916"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019348_16_5411-5460",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "5411-5460",
      "markText": "他隐约感到自己把什么东西遗留在了这里。这些东西或许对他来说十分重要，假如他能知道这究竟是什么东西。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019348&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5411&rangeEnd=5460",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55732e90716e81945571fcf?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5411&rangeEnd=5460"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019348_18_5080-5132",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "5080-5132",
      "markText": "所有这些有什么意义？他又问了一遍自己。即使这，他的——他不想称之为爱——对弗朗辛的渴望，究竟有什么意义？",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019348&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=5080&rangeEnd=5132",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55732e90716e81945571fcf?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=5080&rangeEnd=5132"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019348_16_5166-5218",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "5166-5218",
      "markText": "米勒宣布撤离，紧接着一阵欢欣鼓舞之后，安德鲁斯感到一种异样的悲伤袭上心头，这悲伤像是来自对这地方的留恋。",
      "totalCount": 117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019348&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5166&rangeEnd=5218",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55732e90716e81945571fcf?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5166&rangeEnd=5218"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019348_8_14624-14661",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "14624-14661",
      "markText": "他想该怎么度过这三四天，有没有什么办法将这三四天捏成一团，他可以随手扔掉。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019348&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14624&rangeEnd=14661",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55732e90716e81945571fcf?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14624&rangeEnd=14661"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "24019348_7_7310-7408",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7310-7408",
      "markText": "他意识到他和米勒一起安排的这场捕猎，不过是一种策略，是针对自己的一种谋略，是治疗自己根深蒂固的陋习的一种方法，并没有什么事情促使他来到他现在看到的景色这里和他将要去的地方，他来到这儿完全是不由自主",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=24019348&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7310&rangeEnd=7408",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55732e90716e81945571fcf?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7310&rangeEnd=7408"
